      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "text": "Trait carries the fields that ONLY apply\nin its case. No nullable junk, no \"is\nthis lit?\" branches reading dead fields.\n\nExample:\n  LitBatch {\n    lightCount: number\n    shadowMapRef: Texture\n  }\n\nEntity has LitBatch → has these fields.\nEntity lacks LitBatch → fields don't exist.\nArchetype slab is dense, cache-friendly.",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Trait carries the fields that ONLY apply\nin its case. No nullable junk, no \"is\nthis lit?\" branches reading dead fields.\n\nExample:\n  LitBatch {\n    lightCount: number\n    shadowMapRef: Texture\n  }\n\nEntity has LitBatch → has these fields.\nEntity lacks LitBatch → fields don't exist.\nArchetype slab is dense, cache-friendly.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 11,
      "index": "a5"
    },
