      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "text": "Trait narrows which entities a system\nbodies iterates. System never sees\nunrelated entities.\n\nExample:\n  function animationTickSystem(world) {\n    const animated = world.query(\n      IsAnimated, SpriteUV\n    )\n    for (const e of animated) {\n      // body runs only for animated sprites\n    }\n  }\n\nUse when system body is non-trivial AND\nthe slice is much smaller than total.",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Trait narrows which entities a system\nbodies iterates. System never sees\nunrelated entities.\n\nExample:\n  function animationTickSystem(world) {\n    const animated = world.query(\n      IsAnimated, SpriteUV\n    )\n    for (const e of animated) {\n      // body runs only for animated sprites\n    }\n  }\n\nUse when system body is non-trivial AND\nthe slice is much smaller than total.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 11,
      "index": "a8"
    },
