      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "text": "Bookkeeping — would change with refactors.\nLeaking these is the equivalent of exporting\nprivate fields.\n\n   IsBatched          IsRenderable\n   InBatch(batch)     BatchSlot { batchIdx, slot }\n   BatchMesh          BatchMeta\n   SpriteColor        SpriteUV\n   SpriteFlip         SpriteLayer\n   SpriteMaterialRef\n\nReachable only inside the registry's own\nsystems. No user-callable API returns these.",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Bookkeeping — would change with refactors.\nLeaking these is the equivalent of exporting\nprivate fields.\n\n   IsBatched          IsRenderable\n   InBatch(batch)     BatchSlot { batchIdx, slot }\n   BatchMesh          BatchMeta\n   SpriteColor        SpriteUV\n   SpriteFlip         SpriteLayer\n   SpriteMaterialRef\n\nReachable only inside the registry's own\nsystems. No user-callable API returns these.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 11,
      "index": "aG"
    },
