      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "text": "Rendering classification + opt-in features.\nExposed via facade methods, never as\nKoota imports.\n\n   Batch-level:    IsAlphaBlendedBatch · IsLitBatch\n                   BatchGeometryStrategy { kind }\n   Sprite-level:   IsAnimated · CastsShadow\n                   IsBillboard · IsParticle\n   User-defined:   interface LayerRegistry\n                   (TanStack module augmentation)\n\nAccess:  spriteGroup.layer('fx').batches.where(IsLitBatch)\nNever:   import { IsLitBatch } from 'koota'",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Rendering classification + opt-in features.\nExposed via facade methods, never as\nKoota imports.\n\n   Batch-level:    IsAlphaBlendedBatch · IsLitBatch\n                   BatchGeometryStrategy { kind }\n   Sprite-level:   IsAnimated · CastsShadow\n                   IsBillboard · IsParticle\n   User-defined:   interface LayerRegistry\n                   (TanStack module augmentation)\n\nAccess:  spriteGroup.layer('fx').batches.where(IsLitBatch)\nNever:   import { IsLitBatch } from 'koota'",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 11,
      "index": "aJ"
    },
