      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "text": "System                       Iterates                        Branch predictability      Verdict\n──────────────────────────  ──────────────────────────────  ─────────────────────────  ──────────────────────────\nbatchSortSystem              All active batches (few)        Constant per batch life     Branch on material.transparent\nsceneGraphSyncSystem         All active batches              Perfect                     Branch\nbatchAssignSystem            Newly-added sprites             Per-sprite, varied          Branch (already filtered by Added())\ntransformSyncSystem          Sprites with dirty matrix       Per-sprite                  Branch (already filtered by Changed())\n\nanimationTickSystem          Animated sprites only           N/A — filtered out          ★ Query IsAnimated\nparticleLifecycleSystem      Particles only                  N/A — filtered out          ★ Query IsParticle\nshadowCasterSweep            Casters only                    N/A — filtered out          ★ Query CastsShadow\nbillboardSyncSystem          Billboards only                 N/A — filtered out          ★ Query IsBillboard\n\nTrait existence is the same in both columns.  The query-vs-branch choice is the implementation detail.",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "System                       Iterates                        Branch predictability      Verdict\n──────────────────────────  ──────────────────────────────  ─────────────────────────  ──────────────────────────\nbatchSortSystem              All active batches (few)        Constant per batch life     Branch on material.transparent\nsceneGraphSyncSystem         All active batches              Perfect                     Branch\nbatchAssignSystem            Newly-added sprites             Per-sprite, varied          Branch (already filtered by Added())\ntransformSyncSystem          Sprites with dirty matrix       Per-sprite                  Branch (already filtered by Changed())\n\nanimationTickSystem          Animated sprites only           N/A — filtered out          ★ Query IsAnimated\nparticleLifecycleSystem      Particles only                  N/A — filtered out          ★ Query IsParticle\nshadowCasterSweep            Casters only                    N/A — filtered out          ★ Query CastsShadow\nbillboardSyncSystem          Billboards only                 N/A — filtered out          ★ Query IsBillboard\n\nTrait existence is the same in both columns.  The query-vs-branch choice is the implementation detail.",
